ssageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>A propriedade <strong><code>onlostpointercapture</code></strong> do mixin <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a> é uma <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> que processa eventos <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Reference/Events/lostpointercapture\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">lostpointercapture</a></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>target</em>.onlostpointercapture = <em>functionRef</em>;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>functionRef</code> é o nome de uma função ou uma <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/function\">expressão de função</a>. A função recebe um objeto <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> como seu único argumento.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">overHandler</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Determinar o manipulador lostpointercapture para o evento alvo (target event).</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> lostCaptureHandler <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onlostpointercapture<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> el <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'target'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  el<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onlostpointercapture <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> overHandler<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/pointerevents2/#the-lostpointercapture-event\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Pointer Events – Level 2<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'onlostpointercapture' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.onlostpointercapture","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Evento <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/lostpointercapture_event\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Document: lostpointercapture (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li>Evento <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/lostpointercapture_event\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">HTMLElement: lostpointercapture (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/releasePointerCapture\"><code>Element.releasePointerCapture()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"A propriedade onlostpointercapture do mixin GlobalEventHandlers é uma event handler que processa eventos lostpointercapture.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onlostpointercapture","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element.onlostpointercapture","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onlostpointercapture","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onlostpointercapture","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onlostpointercapture","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onlostpointercapture/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onlostpointercapture"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.onlostpointercapture - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}